@startuml FSW Flight State Machine

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor #555
  FontName Helvetica
  ArrowColor #555
  ArrowFontSize 10
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor #E0C940
  FontSize 10
}

[*] --> Standby : power-on

Standby --> Launch : accel_mag > LAUNCH_ACCEL_G\nOR baro_alt_rise > LAUNCH_BARO_RISE_M\nfor >= LAUNCH_WINDOW_S s

Launch --> Ascent : baro_alt_m > ASCENT_ALT_M\nOR gps_vvel_mps > ASCENT_VVEL_MPS\nfor >= ASCENT_WINDOW_S s

Ascent --> Cruise : gps_vvel_mps < CRUISE_VVEL_MPS\nOR baro_alt_delta_m < CRUISE_ALT_BAND_M\nfor >= CRUISE_WINDOW_S s

Ascent --> Descent : [cruise skip]\naccel_delta_g > DESCENT_ACCEL_DELTA_G\nOR gps_vvel_mps < DESCENT_VVEL_MPS\nfor >= DESCENT_WINDOW_S s

Cruise --> Descent : accel_delta_g > DESCENT_ACCEL_DELTA_G\nOR gps_vvel_mps < DESCENT_VVEL_MPS\nfor >= DESCENT_WINDOW_S s

Descent --> Landing : gps_speed_mps < LANDING_SPEED_MPS\nOR baro_alt_m < LANDING_ALT_M\nfor >= LANDING_WINDOW_S s

Landing --> [*] : terminal state

note right of Standby
  Record ground pressure baseline.
  All baro altitudes relative to this.
end note

note right of Cruise
  Track running IMU median as float
  baseline for relative burst detection.
end note

note right of Landing
  Shutdown timer starts on entry.
  Logging and telemetry continue
  for recovery.
end note

@enduml
